{"tid":654633,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)每日電腦一開機就有畫面死咗情況","createTime":"2018-05-05T19:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:59:32.000Z","uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe85f23b8a96887187f3db5fef3c68beef5a5b44","tid":654633,"uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:53:04.000Z","msg":"開咗部機無幾耐 就會個畫面郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個滑鼠鼠標冇反應,Keyboard caps lock冇反應等等)<br />\n成部機停咗係到 <br />\n雖然重新開機之後係冇事 但係我驚部機遲吓咁樣耐去會壞<br />\n<br />\n想請教大家如果咁樣多數會係啲咩問題出事??<br />\n<br />\n利申 上個月換咗8700k+底版 <br />\n本來用緊AMD, AMD嗰陣冇依個問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我拍咗片大慨發生咗咩事 但唔識upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都同我上面講嘅差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fca55393f8b77b1a8c81b9fdc79d372b79ee717","tid":654633,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d770beccf943745af5751f6225afadad0818ae7","tid":654633,"uid":31705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:50:56.000Z","msg":"有冇試過用內置顯示卡插槽 同插你外置有咩分別"},{"pid":"27a508a4afccab5602131f1fa7f380bf3711fa95","tid":654633,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"係咪win10?"},{"pid":"64fdd3fb6c6f2d3cb5a0b7f6b5cca7444bdc8d75","tid":654633,"uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d770beccf943745af5751f6225afadad0818ae7","tid":654633,"uid":31705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:50:56.000Z","msg":"有冇試過用內置顯示卡插槽 同插你外置有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"未試過  如果內置插槽冇事 = 顯示卡問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dea80c375b717a5a1b70ece09c7b4a55c8dba